Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.29,0:00:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.83,0:00:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢無止盡的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.13,0:00:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像往常一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.80,0:00:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在往常的場所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.87,0:00:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能等待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.11,0:00:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.47,0:00:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.81,0:00:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在也在等待著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.61,0:00:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有時間的黃昏的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.88,0:01:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進行著一段永遠的旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.76,0:01:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷的指尖繼續探索著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.24,0:01:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碎片發出光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.51,0:01:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緊緊的抱住胸口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.72,0:01:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尋找遺失的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.86,0:01:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用雙手的掌心確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.20,0:01:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相遇在新的早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.57,0:01:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間開始流動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.95,0:02:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「夜裡」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.31,0:02:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.21,0:02:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的臉怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.45,0:02:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是跌到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.25,0:02:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想爬過校門但是失敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.49,0:02:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.99,0:02:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面很冷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.76,0:02:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浴室沒有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.13,0:02:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.12,0:03:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是夢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.33,0:03:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太超脫現實的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.84,0:03:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看不見的怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.61,0:03:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿著劍戰鬥的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.75,0:03:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是打擊惡魔之人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.35,0:03:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.95,0:04:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚了怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.62,0:04:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是妳！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.36,0:04:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.47,0:04:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.11,0:04:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是蒟蒻吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.51,0:04:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳拿著那個想做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.22,0:04:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.85,0:04:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我肚子餓了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.09,0:05:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼晚了\N我還得跟妳一起吃蒟蒻呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.37,0:05:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.74,0:05:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為晚飯不夠吃吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.94,0:05:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們現在正在發育
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.31,0:05:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來還是應該多做一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.11,0:05:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是秋子阿姨的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.02,0:05:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我現在就去作宵夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.02,0:05:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我肚子不餓…\N不是啦 我是說雖然餓…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.53,0:05:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別人的好意妳就接受吧\N就這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.47,0:05:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 老是喜歡搞飛機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.46,0:06:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.86,0:06:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好像不舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.79,0:06:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胃不舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.66,0:06:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫妳要吃宵夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.43,0:06:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒有要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.03,0:06:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是祐一你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.10,0:06:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我？怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.17,0:06:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這麼健忘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.29,0:06:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.89,0:06:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.66,0:06:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你從昨晚開始就怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.56,0:06:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.73,0:06:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安\N早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.90,0:06:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臉怎麼了？\N刮鬍子弄的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.27,0:06:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這間學校有什麼奇怪的傳聞嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.04,0:06:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的傳聞？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.31,0:07:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,例如像晚上會出現什麼鬼怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.35,0:07:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是有拿著劍的女孩子\N在學校走動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.95,0:07:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.95,0:07:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.75,0:07:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廁所的花子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.02,0:07:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有詛咒的鋼琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.02,0:07:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在晚上走動的人體模型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.09,0:07:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那種的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.86,0:07:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定是睡呆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.29,0:07:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說的是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.60,0:07:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天晚上真的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.94,0:07:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相澤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.04,0:07:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安 昨天晚上謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.21,0:07:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不記得我了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.32,0:07:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.22,0:07:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.59,0:07:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你認識她嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.76,0:07:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是三年級的川澄舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.90,0:07:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我勸你少接近她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.23,0:07:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.74,0:07:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.32,0:08:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們來晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.66,0:08:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把人趕走的話\N至少會有一張空桌子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.49,0:08:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以趕人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.40,0:08:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有位子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.63,0:08:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡可以吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.14,0:08:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.21,0:08:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼 只是想要坐在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.37,0:08:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相澤 別這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.48,0:08:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.74,0:08:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他是轉學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.55,0:08:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.45,0:08:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 他是學生會長久瀨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.25,0:08:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是惹上了他以後就有苦頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.52,0:08:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.55,0:08:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他是本地士紳的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.89,0:08:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此到處都吃的開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.59,0:08:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以很多人向他獻殷勤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.36,0:08:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼年代了還有這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.66,0:08:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也不想承認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.36,0:09:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有山犬誤闖進學校了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.17,0:09:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的確跟我以前住過的地方\N不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.09,0:09:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,栞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.66,0:09:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.57,0:09:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,栞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.73,0:09:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.64,0:09:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪 快帶著她逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.41,0:09:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.27,0:09:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說了 快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.31,0:09:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.51,0:09:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.85,0:09:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,栞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.44,0:10:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.11,0:10:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經通知了捕狗大隊 放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.28,0:10:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川澄 妳要去哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.75,0:10:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說說看 要是受傷了怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.72,0:10:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是來救我們的\N這樣說未免太…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.82,0:10:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.62,0:10:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 老是惹麻煩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.93,0:10:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我還沒說完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.53,0:10:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川澄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.03,0:10:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.43,0:10:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳從後門離開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.03,0:10:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是連妳都被追究起來\N就不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.77,0:10:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.87,0:10:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.61,0:10:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 你認識她嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.31,0:10:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 妳先去吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.95,0:11:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相澤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.54,0:11:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來妳在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.21,0:11:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 至少讓我道謝一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.35,0:11:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳救了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.69,0:11:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是第二次被妳救了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.16,0:11:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不害怕嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.76,0:11:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是跟昨晚的東西比起來\N根本不算什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.97,0:11:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為牠只是肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.70,0:11:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牠只是肚子餓\N才變得暴躁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.44,0:12:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這隻狗以前也曾經為了找吃的\N進來學校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.58,0:12:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.75,0:12:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倉田佐佑理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.58,0:12:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你認識小舞嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.72,0:12:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不認識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.65,0:12:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不認識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.36,0:12:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 我們昨晚第一次見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.96,0:12:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人因此墜入愛河嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.63,0:12:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.30,0:12:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.30,0:12:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞 自我介紹一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.77,0:12:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川澄舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.47,0:12:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是相澤祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.14,0:12:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相澤同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.44,0:12:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我相澤就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.78,0:12:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳是我的學姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.55,0:12:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫名字就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.78,0:12:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.59,0:12:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 你還沒有吃午飯吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.46,0:12:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方便的話我們一起吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.09,0:12:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…\N我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.14,0:13:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃飯是不錯啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.87,0:13:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼要在這種地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.04,0:13:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這樣比在桌上更好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.11,0:13:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道妳們平常都這樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.12,0:13:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.02,0:13:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平常都是吃便當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.95,0:13:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是剛才餵狗吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.22,0:13:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太可惜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.26,0:13:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要給狗吃不如給我吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.49,0:13:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那明天開始我也幫你帶便當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.10,0:13:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不太好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.37,0:13:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.37,0:13:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的便當可是廣受好評的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.51,0:13:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞 妳說對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.04,0:13:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從以前就這樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.78,0:13:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從第一次見面時開始就這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.45,0:13:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.28,0:13:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 從入學開始以來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.69,0:13:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到妳們能成為朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.46,0:13:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也是朋友了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.37,0:14:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來還是沒有問她\N昨晚的事情嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.27,0:14:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是打擊惡魔之人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.47,0:14:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且不知道佐佑理\N知道那個鬼怪的事情嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.55,0:14:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.65,0:14:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能沒事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.19,0:14:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我感覺有殺氣\N所以不自覺的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.49,0:14:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有什麼殺氣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.39,0:14:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要不要去學柔道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.40,0:14:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還能學會怎麼摔比較不痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.00,0:14:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.20,0:14:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳老是出現在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.00,0:14:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你這麼閒嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.84,0:14:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是閒 我是來找東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.74,0:14:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 妳好像說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.78,0:14:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有找到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.28,0:14:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.35,0:14:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.55,0:14:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛好我也有點郁悶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.15,0:14:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.39,0:14:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.62,0:15:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之只要依照妳平常的路線找\N應該會有線索吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.00,0:15:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,附近有哪裡是妳最常去的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.04,0:15:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那邊轉角賣甜食的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.14,0:15:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,點心店吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.77,0:15:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.51,0:15:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.64,0:15:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要不要先准備鏟子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.91,0:15:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為要挖掘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.02,0:15:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道妳在找的是\N埋在地底的寶藏嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.92,0:15:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.33,0:15:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“點心坊”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.30,0:15:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“麥當勞”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.51,0:15:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“鯛魚燒”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.71,0:15:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“可麗餅”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.08,0:15:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.92,0:16:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.29,0:16:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我不知道的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.49,0:16:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可麗餅的總類變多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.62,0:16:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.72,0:16:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.56,0:16:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是認真還是在騙\N我二選一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.30,0:16:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是認真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.50,0:16:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一個地方呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.60,0:16:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前面的蛋糕店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.04,0:16:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼都是一些賣吃的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.60,0:16:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少管我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.51,0:16:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.24,0:16:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.81,0:16:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡應該有一間蛋糕店的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.38,0:16:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.19,0:16:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是沒有線索嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.36,0:16:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提起精神來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.76,0:16:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去買鯛魚燒來吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.06,0:16:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.64,0:16:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的也給妳吃吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.27,0:16:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.54,0:17:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.84,0:17:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看妳剛才還一副要死不活的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.72,0:17:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子肚子餓了\N就提不起精神了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.69,0:17:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.99,0:17:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.82,0:17:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.36,0:17:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明天也會繼續努力的尋找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.13,0:17:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.50,0:17:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了就提不起精神嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.04,0:17:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.31,0:17:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要出門嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.88,0:17:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出去一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.71,0:17:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.08,0:17:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.02,0:17:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.12,0:17:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可疑什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.29,0:17:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼不可告人的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.89,0:17:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼傻話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.32,0:17:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且跟妳無關吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.86,0:17:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.93,0:17:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.54,0:18:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳果然在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.11,0:18:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是帶給妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.68,0:18:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“竹屋牛肉飯”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.68,0:18:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這不足以\N感謝妳白天救了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.02,0:18:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子不餓嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.15,0:18:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回答我一下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.79,0:18:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳餓還是不餓？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.33,0:18:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.93,0:18:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.96,0:18:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.03,0:18:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜歡牛肉飯嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.20,0:18:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.73,0:18:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？那就太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.97,0:18:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快趁熱吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.44,0:18:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.74,0:18:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓋子打開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.68,0:18:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有筷子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.99,0:18:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劍放下來不就好了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.03,0:18:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.30,0:18:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.53,0:19:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.80,0:19:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓果然會提不起精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.37,0:19:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.51,0:19:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼來這裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.51,0:19:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是想來確定一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.18,0:19:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確定？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.08,0:19:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要親眼確定\N昨天晚上看到的不是做夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.58,0:19:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有那個鬼怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.82,0:19:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及跟妳在這裡相遇的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.13,0:19:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是做夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.46,0:19:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.50,0:19:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒出現而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.77,0:19:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.84,0:19:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是要我幫妳\N拿著這碗牛肉飯嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.38,0:19:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼也幫不上忙嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.05,0:19:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只能在這裡看著嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.18,0:19:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.39,0:20:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只一隻嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.19,0:20:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.13,0:20:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.29,0:20:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑掉了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.63,0:20:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.67,0:20:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之能平安太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.57,0:20:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.31,0:20:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳覺得牛肉飯比我更重要嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.65,0:21:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.52,0:21:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少騙人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.52,0:21:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳那是什麼眼神？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.05,0:21:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.99,0:21:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這傢伙承認了？\N終於承認了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.00,0:21:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.33,0:21:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要把這裡清理一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.67,0:21:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.07,0:21:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.64,0:21:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看不見的鬼怪是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.78,0:21:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞又為何而戰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.05,0:21:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.18,0:21:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是小舞的那句道謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.89,0:21:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻比什麼都更來的讓我高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.10,0:21:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.63,0:21:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相澤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.63,0:21:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早 怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.80,0:21:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.67,0:21:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是飆車族？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.47,0:21:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是川澄幹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.67,0:21:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人看到她昨晚在學校\N拿著類似鐵管的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.51,0:22:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.25,0:22:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川澄同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.25,0:22:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有事情找妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.55,0:22:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以跟我們來一下嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.50,0:22:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從隨風飄流的雲朵之間\N窺視到晴空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.45,0:22:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就連熟悉的街道也閃閃發光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.82,0:22:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向前奔跑的小小的背影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.16,0:22:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時的兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.07,0:23:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用天真來蓋過溢出的疼痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.08,0:23:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間靜悄悄的流動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.59,0:23:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吹拂著溫柔的風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.03,0:23:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為凍僵的思念也會化做笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.31,0:23:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞的惡作劇過份了一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.38,0:23:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是那就像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.51,0:23:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為吃不到樹上的葡萄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.38,0:23:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而鬧彆扭的小狐狸的模樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.48,0:23:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanon第5話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.29,0:23:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狐狸與葡萄
